data.title: St Paul's Evangelical Country Church 11055 Dumfries Ave. Council Bluffs, Iowa 51
data.meta_description: St Paul's Evangelical Country Church preaches & teaches the Bible. It is the complete truth. We believe Jesus is the Son of God and we believe He is the only way to heaven. We love God and one another. We are committed to the Great Commission. We believe Jesus is coming back again soon.
data.text:
Matthew 28:18-20 " Then Jesus came to them and said, 'All authority in heaven and on earth has been given to me. Therefore go and make disciples of all nations, baptizing them in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, and teaching them to obey everything I have commanded you. And surely I am with you always, to the very end of the age.”

​

St. Paul's is committed to God's Word and spreading the gospel in our community and around the world. We emphasize the importance of sharing Jesus with our family and friends and to show His love and compassion in times of need. We support a number of local ministries and give to missionaries around the world.

We take prayer seriously at St Paul's

so we make it a priority to

intercede for others in prayer.

​

God cares about our every need and

He tells us not worry but to pray.

​

Philippians 4:6

"Do not be anxious about anything,

but in everything by prayer and supplication

with thanksgiving let your requests

be made known to God."

​

​
